  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the claypot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion, carrot, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the cubed white yam, apple cider vinegar, salt, black pepper, and turmeric to the claypot.",
    "Stir well to combine and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes or until the yam is tender.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
